
 -0 StatsD - NodeJS Daemon
------------------------
  > Listens for messages over a UDP port & extracts metrics. 
  > The extracted metrics are then dumped to Graphite for further processing & visualization.

 -0 Monitoring with syslog & EventMachine
----------------------------------------------
  > Build syslog server via EventSource -UDP : 514 --> EventAggregator -> Dashboard
  > or EventSource -> UDP : 514 --> Syslog -forward--> EventAggregator -> Dashboard
  > Syslog Server = Listen on UDP or tail a log file -> rx & parse syslog message
  > Rx & Parse syslog using EventMachine in ur custom Syslog server
  > EventSource -> ServerSentEvent

